<L>__{interior hayatsus minivan day}
<A>__{ryuji and asakawa sit in the back. mr. hayatsu is behind the wheel, chattering away.}
<C>__{hayatsu}
<D>__{back in the old days, the yamamuras used to head fishing boats out in sashikiji, though they dont much anymore. you know, one of shizukos cousins is still alive. hes just an old man now. his son and his daughter in law run an old fashioned inn. i went ahead and booked reservations for yall, hope thats alright...}
<A>__{asakawa gives the briefest of nods in reply, after which the minivan lapses into silence. asakawa looks dreamily out at the mountain studded landscape, then suddenly snaps to.}
<C>__{asakawa}
<P>__{(to ryuji)}
<D>__{why did yamamura shizuko commit suicide?}
<C>__{ryuji}
<D>__{she was taking a real beating in the press, being called a fraud and all sorts of names. after a while she just lost it.}
